text:
On Saturday, dozens of houses in the center of Krasnoyarsk will turn off cold water

01 Nov 2019, 08:40

Tatyana Lukina, a spokeswoman for KrasKom, said that tomorrow, November 2, there will be no cold water in the houses of the Central District of Krasnoyarsk.
The water will be shut off from 10 a.m. to 5 p.m. in order to change the emergency valve on the water supply at the intersection of ul. Lenin and st. Surikov.
There will be no cold water at the following addresses:

D. Proletariat, 40a, 35, 39;
Mira, 46a, 46g, 36, 32, 34;
Surikova, 65, 67;
Lenin, 74, 74 pages 2, 74g pages 1, 76, 76 pages 3, 76 pages 1, 80, 113a, 113, 111, 73, 80a, 3a, 69, 64, 54, 49, 52, 36, 34, 23, 21, 28, 26, 11, 5a;
